  "name": "Ki Block",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/items/weapons/kunai.png",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A ninja with this trick can prevent a creature from using its&nbsp;ki&nbsp;pool. Whenever the ninja deals sneak attack damage, the target must make a Will save or be unable to spend any points from its&nbsp;ki&nbsp;pool for a number of rounds equal to the ninja's Charisma modifier. The DC of this save is 10 + 1/2 the ninja's level + the ninja's Charisma modifier. The number of points in the target's&nbsp;ki&nbsp;pool is unaffected, and abilities that do not require the subject to spend&nbsp;ki&nbsp;still function.</p>"
    },
